#: index.docbook:322
msgid "Requirements"
msgstr "Requerimientos"

#: index.docbook:324
msgid ""
"You will need to have the kdelibs package installed in order to successfully "
"compile the kdetoys package that contains &amor;. The kdelibs package may be "
"found at the same location as the kdetoys package."
msgstr ""
"Necesitará tener el paquete kdelibs instalado para poder compilar el "
"paquete kdetoys el cual contiene &amor;. El paquete kdetoys puede ser "
"encontrado en el mismo lugar que el paquete kdetoys."

#: index.docbook:331
msgid "Compilation and Installation"
msgstr "Compilación e instalación"

#: index.docbook:333
msgid ""
"In order to compile and install &amor; on your system, type the following in "
"the top-level kdetoys directory in the kdetoys distribution:"
msgstr ""
"Para compilar e instalar &amor; en sus sistema, escriba lo siguiente en el "
"directorio principal de kdetoys del paquete kdetoys:"

#: index.docbook:337
msgid ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>./configure</command></userinput>\n"
"<prompt>%</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:340
msgid ""
"At this point, you can either install the entire kdetoys package, or just "
"install &amor;. To install only &amor;, first change to the amor directory. "
"To install the entire package, remain in the kdetoys directory."
msgstr ""
"En este punto, usted puede instalar el paquete kdetoys entero o sólo "
"instalar &amor;. Para instalar sólamente &amor;, primero cambie al "
"directorio de amor. Para instalar el paquete completo, continue en el "
"directorio kdetoys."

#: index.docbook:345
msgid ""
"In either case, you will likely need to become <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>"
" before installing. Once you have become <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem>, type the following:"
msgstr ""
"En cualquier caso, necesitará convertirse en <systemitem "
"class=\"username\">root</systemitem> antes de instlarlo. Una vez sea "
"<systemitem class=\"username\">root</systemitem>, escriba lo siguiente:"

#: index.docbook:350
msgid ""
"<prompt>#</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"<prompt>#</prompt> <userinput><command>make</command> "
"<option>install</option></userinput>"

#: index.docbook:352
msgid ""
"Compiling and installing the required kdelibs package follows the same "
"process. If you encounter any problems compiling or installing &amor;, help "
"may be obtained from the <ulink "
"url=\"http://www.kde.org/mailinglists.html\">&kde; mailing lists </ulink>"
" or from the Usenet newsgroup: comp.windows.x.kde."
msgstr ""
"Compilar e instalar el paquete kdelibs, necesario, sigue el mismo preoceso. "
"Si tiene algún problema compilando o instalando &amor;, puede consegui "
"ayuda de <ulink url=\"http://www.kde.org/mailinglists.html\">las listas de "
"correo de &kde;</ulink> o del grupo Usenet de discursión :  "
"comp.windows.x.kde."
